        "text": "Brenna was amazing to work with! I found her last minute with a super quick turn around time and little hope I would be able to pull everything off, she reached out immediately and helped me plan the whole thing which was a ginormous comfort. I keep joking that she was our engagement planner, she went above and beyond making sure everything went perfectly including listening to my constant anxieties and paranoia that arose. The turn around was so quick for the photos, and we’ve been amazed with every one. Thank you Brenna!"
      },
      {
